originalText.text: The session with Rosalie was profoundly spiritual and helped me reset after feeling depleted from emotional disarray. She taps her intuitiveness and instruments, like sound bowls, to expand the reiki experience. I am deeply grateful that she has chosen to share her knowledge and gifts. I highly recommend!

originalText.text: This was nothing less than an awakening, an intense journey to the center. Rosalie created a richly textured immersive experience, sharing her own energy as well as energy from crystals, aromas, music... I was transported and released with gentle but determined waves of guidance and I am now changed. This was my first 'formal' experience with Reiki and it will not be my last. Avail yourself of Rosalie. Give yourself that gift.

originalText.text: This is an easy 5 star recommendation. The level of communication was exceptional from start to finish. It was my first Reiki session and I went in being rather skeptical, but now I have no doubts. Rosalie provided powerful insights that were reassuring. When I left the session my vision was clear, I felt mental clarity, and could breathe better. The following day I was exhausted, but now it's been several days and I feel invigorated and balanced. Rosalie is incredibly skilled. She sent me a follow up email with recommendations and I cannot express how grateful I am that I had booked an appointment with her. The center itself is beautiful and soothing.

originalText.text: If there were 100 stars to give, that would be my rating. This experience was different than anything I’ve ever experienced. I’ve spoken to a medium several times, but the sense of feeling holds more than just the sense of hearing. My experience has continued after my session, helping me connect to my emotions more and letting it go. The days that followed still felt intense, in a good and much needed way. I have a tendency to unconsciously hold my emotions in, after this it just flowed in its own. I can't thank you enough! Going to book another appointment soon.

originalText.text: Rosalie is simply amazing ! Her space is so calming and comforting, and her energy and presence are even more so! She immediately made me feel comfortable and within minutes i was sharing feelings and emotions with her that i’ve never shared with anyone before! I’ve done Reiki before, but this was my first time with Rosalie. And I have to say that this session felt so powerful. After the session, I immediately felt lighter! And immediately felt like a weight was lifted off of my chest! I even called her a week later for some advice and she did not hesitate to get on the phone with me and help me overcome some residual anxiety that i was feeling from the session! She is truly, truly gifted and is amazing at what she does!
